A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Law Enforcement Officers’ Pension System – Forest Heights Police Department
3 – Membership
4 FOR the purpose of authorizing certain law enforcement employees of the Forest Heights
5 Police Department to participate in the Law Enforcement Officers’ Pension System;
6 providing that membership in the Law Enforcement Officers’ Pension System is
7 optional for certain employees of the Forest Heights Police Department; requiring
8 certain employees of the Forest Heights Police Department to make a certain election
9 on a certain date; providing for certain employees of the Forest Heights Police
10 Department to receive service credit for certain prior service; providing that certain
11 employees of the Forest Heights Police Department who become members of the Law
12 Enforcement Officers’ Pension System after a certain date may not receive certain
13 service credit; and generally relating to employees of the Forest Heights Police
14 Department participating in the Law Enforcement Officers’ Pension System.
